  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Epiphrenic III Pilot Trial investigates whether a diaphragmatic stimulation by
      interventionally placed electrodes may improve heart function, symptoms and functional
      capacity in patients with severe heart failure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
